Subject: Re: [T2] brakes stuck

Putting antisieze on the threads will also prevent the theads from galling - 
especially if high tightening torque is applied.

Just remember to put a light amount.

I have had really good luck with a ceramic based paste called Rock 'n Roll.

Use it on everything. Good for up to 2500 deg F. 
